{"tid":809073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國軍艦據報駛近西沙群島","createTime":"2018-09-07T00:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T00:58:23.000Z","uid":56015,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49f290cb9cccc9220e61a8eb6cba694a9b89f076","tid":809073,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"【英國軍艦據報駛近西沙群島】<br />\n【中方派出艦隻監控】<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》引述消息人士報道，英國海軍船塢登陸艦「海神之子號」 (HMS Albion)，近日前往越南途中，駛過具主權爭議的西沙群島。<br />\n<br />\n中國派出一艘護衛艦及兩架直升機，監控英方艦艇，雙方期間保持克制。<br />\n<br />\n另一名消息人士指，英國艦隻沒有進入受爭議海域。<br />\n<br />\n英國海軍發言人表示，「海神之子號」依照國際法行使航行自由的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/1846190398828317/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F1846190398828317%2F&d=9b3%2B2YHVjZQkmEDiOr2KC7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=5fe9c5b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/1846190398828317/</a>"},{"pid":"06380b5d1a5999bf06572d4f51ed0d6769f48b70","tid":809073,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:48:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-britain-china-southchinasea-exclusive/exclusive-british-navy-warship-sails-near-south-china-sea-islands-angering-beijing-idUSKCN1LM017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-britain-china-southchinasea-exclusive%2Fexclusive-british-navy-warship-sails-near-south-china-sea-islands-angering-beijing-idUSKCN1LM017&d=9b3%2B2YHVjZQkmEDiOr2KC7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=730375fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-britain-china-southchinasea-exclusive%2Fexclusive-british-navy-warship-sails-near-south-china-sea-islands-angering-beijing-idUSKCN1LM017&h=72fc15ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-britain-china-southchinasea-exclusive/exclusive-british-navy-warship-sails-near-so